    ps.pointer += 1
    while ps.at? ' ' do
      ps.pointer += 1
    end
    stack.last.content.push OpenStruct.new(type: :space)


We'll consider the [[U+00A0 NO-BREAK SPACE]] a form of markup.
Each such character will be a node of the type [[:nbsp]], with
no attributes.

<< Parse a bit of markup >>:
