    margin-top: 0
    margin-bottom: 0

  .maui-chunk
    margin-top: $paragraph-sep
    margin-bottom: $paragraph-sep


The cross-references following (final) chunks are smaller and in
italic for reduced obtrusivity, and they align with the chunk's
